column5: So, I've just spent about 1.5hrs of my life, that I'll NEVER get back...Saw the movie QUARANTINE....  Just wanted to know what YOU (to those who've watched it) thought of the movie?
Has anyone tried that new horseradish flavoured mustard?
LOL.... sorry, I'm just a lil' p*ssed off @ this stupid movie...
well spank my nuts and call me murphy. You should have watched the ufc fights instead. I haven watched the movie but i want to.
i thought it was decent... not awful, not great
What REALLY annoyed me about the movie....well, I won't spoil it....but, it annoyed me.

i agree with you its a bad movie. If you want to watch those movies that are like taken by a camcorder, cloverfield is MUCH better.  And yes, UFC would have been a good choice tonight, except their main event kinda sucked.
yeah i expected more out of diego. He almost looked anorexic trying to be in the 155 weight class.
Here’s an artist’s conception of  Diego "The Nightmare" Sanchez  at his new weight. -TheGarve.Com
